  "detailed_description": "Galaia is a small Action-Adventure Roguelite made with love for both roguelite fans and newcomers to the genre!<br><br>Centuries have passed since The Flood destroyed the mighty kingdom of Galaia. Atop of the wreckage, only the Last Ruins remain, and among them the answers to what happened.<br><br>Venture time and time again into the ever-changing ruins of Galaia defeating enemies, exploring enigmatic locations, and uncovering secrets until you collect all the powerful Relics hidden inside!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COZY ROGUELITE</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/9b32bd1c7e886925a85baa043280a2b3.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/9b32bd1c7e886925a85baa043280a2b3.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/9b32bd1c7e886925a85baa043280a2b3.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Galaia is very <strong>welcoming to newcomers</strong> to the genre while still offering <strong>challenges to the most veteran roguelike players</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAST AND FUN COMBAT</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/5a9473a0adaa3b7702c36fa760807896.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/5a9473a0adaa3b7702c36fa760807896.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/5a9473a0adaa3b7702c36fa760807896.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Galaia's combat is straight up shooter fun, very focused on <strong>mobility and synergies</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MORE THAN MEETS THE EYE</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/37e6417b29d47d2af835877bbefc0d33.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/37e6417b29d47d2af835877bbefc0d33.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/37e6417b29d47d2af835877bbefc0d33.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Not everything is combat! The mysterious ruins hide many <strong>secrets and collectibles</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COME AND JOIN THE ADVENTURE!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/26ded1a200ccc228a93ee2ee50cdacc9.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/26ded1a200ccc228a93ee2ee50cdacc9.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/26ded1a200ccc228a93ee2ee50cdacc9.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>What are you waiting for? Galaia awaits!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's Note</h2><i>Galaia has been developed by <strong>just one person</strong> over 4 years! As such, it has been impossible for me to add as many content to the game as the other amazing big roguelike titles. However <strong>lots of love</strong> and care have been put in this game, so others can experience the game that I always wanted to make and play.<br><br>I'm very conscious of player's time and money, so I tried to price the game fairly for what it has to offer. Expect around a short fun game with a very replayable structure. </i><br><br>I sincerely hope you enjoy the game as much as I enjoyed making it!",
  "about_the_game": "Galaia is a small Action-Adventure Roguelite made with love for both roguelite fans and newcomers to the genre!<br><br>Centuries have passed since The Flood destroyed the mighty kingdom of Galaia. Atop of the wreckage, only the Last Ruins remain, and among them the answers to what happened.<br><br>Venture time and time again into the ever-changing ruins of Galaia defeating enemies, exploring enigmatic locations, and uncovering secrets until you collect all the powerful Relics hidden inside!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COZY ROGUELITE</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/9b32bd1c7e886925a85baa043280a2b3.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/9b32bd1c7e886925a85baa043280a2b3.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/9b32bd1c7e886925a85baa043280a2b3.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Galaia is very <strong>welcoming to newcomers</strong> to the genre while still offering <strong>challenges to the most veteran roguelike players</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAST AND FUN COMBAT</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/5a9473a0adaa3b7702c36fa760807896.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/5a9473a0adaa3b7702c36fa760807896.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/5a9473a0adaa3b7702c36fa760807896.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Galaia's combat is straight up shooter fun, very focused on <strong>mobility and synergies</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MORE THAN MEETS THE EYE</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/37e6417b29d47d2af835877bbefc0d33.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/37e6417b29d47d2af835877bbefc0d33.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/37e6417b29d47d2af835877bbefc0d33.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Not everything is combat! The mysterious ruins hide many <strong>secrets and collectibles</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COME AND JOIN THE ADVENTURE!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/26ded1a200ccc228a93ee2ee50cdacc9.poster.avif?t=1721318430\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/26ded1a200ccc228a93ee2ee50cdacc9.webm?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625930/extras/26ded1a200ccc228a93ee2ee50cdacc9.mp4?t=1721318430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>What are you waiting for? Galaia awaits!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's Note</h2><i>Galaia has been developed by <strong>just one person</strong> over 4 years! As such, it has been impossible for me to add as many content to the game as the other amazing big roguelike titles. However <strong>lots of love</strong> and care have been put in this game, so others can experience the game that I always wanted to make and play.<br><br>I'm very conscious of player's time and money, so I tried to price the game fairly for what it has to offer. Expect around a short fun game with a very replayable structure. </i><br><br>I sincerely hope you enjoy the game as much as I enjoyed making it!",
